text: Hey Jon, just to clarify does this happen if you copy the same module again, or can it happen if you copy a different module in the same  folder?
I’ve only done it with a different module, I would suspect it would happen either way though as once the folder has been created and deleted it should be in that same broken state

Hmmmm okay. I can’t reproduce it with different modules but can when it’s the same module. I think if you already have a copy of that module anywhere in your finder then it won’t copy over since the moduleIds are the same.
<@U26D0TF8E> feel free to DM me with your portalId and specific template that you are trying to copy a well as destination portal
